 \\ &&
 +\int_0^\beta\frac{\alpha\sigma}{(\alpha^2-\sigma^2)^2}G(\alpha,\sigma)d\sigma.\quad
 \end{eqnarray}
 and integrating again in $\alpha$ from $\beta$ to $\alpha$:
