\sqrt{\bar \lambda(\alpha^2-\beta^2)} \frac{\mathrm{I_1}\left[2\sqrt{\bar \lambda \alpha \beta}\right]}{\sqrt{\alpha \beta}}.
 \end{eqnarray}
Substituting $\alpha$ and $\beta$ by the physical variables $r$, $\rho$, it is found that
   \begin{eqnarray}
 \vert G\vert &\leq&
